# Instruqt + Git

This repository is the **Instruqt track** source (`paypal-elastic-serverless`).

Whenever you **commit and push to Git** (`git push`) for this project, also run **`instruqt track push`** from **this directory** (the repo root that contains `track.yml`), unless the user explicitly says not to.

```bash
cd "$(git rev-parse --show-toplevel)" && instruqt track push
```

If `instruqt track push` fails (auth, network), report the error and what the user should run locally.

Track manager URL: https://play.instruqt.com/manage/elastic/tracks/paypal-elastic-serverless
